Usage

varnames

vector of indicator variables names from blockgroupstats, bgej, etc., such as "pm", "pctlowinc", "pctile.EJ.DISPARITY.traffic.score.eo" etc. and others as found in names_all_r, or specific subsets of those like in c(names_d, names_d_subgroups, names_e) and c(names_ej_pctile, names_ej_state_pctile, names_ej_supp_pctile, names_ej_supp_state_pctile)

s1

name of column in map_headernames to get sort info from

s2

optional like s1 but secondary to s1

s3

optional tertiary

Value

vector as from order(), to be used in sorting a data.frame for example
